\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπηλλαγμένα [ἴχνη]</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg014.perseus-grc1:8:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.3</biblScope> </bibl>); of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καρχαρόδοντα, ἐ. τοὺς ὀδόντας</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have</tr_> their teeth <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fitting in</tr_> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">like</abbr> two saws, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:501a:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">501a18</biblScope> </bibl>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, [<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">νεῦρα] ἀλλήλοισι ἐπαλλαξάμενα ἐς χιασμὸν σχήματος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0719.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aret.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SD\">SD</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.7</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cross one another,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δόρατα . . ὡς ἥκιστα ἂν ἀλλήλοις ἐπαλλάττοιτο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg012.perseus-grc1:3:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.Mag.\">Eq.Mag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.3</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπηλλαγμέναις δι᾽ ἀλ